data.description: Come check out this beautiful, very well- maintained spacious, 4-bedrooms, 2-bath brick home, located in the CHEROKEE ROSE COUNTRY CLUB and centrally located to Fort Stewart, Hunter Army Airfield, Schools, Restaurants, and Shopping Centers. The home features a foyer entrance, living room, formal dining, family room with a fireplace, Gorgeous eat-in kitchen, and landscaped yard. The home also, comes with the following updates: A new HVAC system in 2022, A new Roof in 2017, A new updated kitchen in 2023 with new Double Ovens/Countertops and all new Stainless-Steel Appliances, new flooring in 2022, newly painted interior in 2023, and new upgraded bathrooms in 2023. The home is located on the Golf course hole # 1 and comes with 2-Storage Sheds.
